text: Matos or Mattos may refer to: ==Places== * Mattos, California, in Alameda County * Salir de Matos, a parish in the municipality of Caldas da Rainha, Portugal * Matos River, a river in Bolivia * Matos Costa, a municipality in the Brazilian state of Santa Catarina ==Other uses== * Matos (surname) * Matot or matos or (Hebrew מטות), the 42nd weekly parshah in the cycle of Torah reading * Matorral or mato, the scrublands, or heaths, of Portugal == See also == * Mata (disambiguation) * Matus * Mato (disambiguation) * Mattō, Ishikawa * Atos
title: Matos
